item.title: Merry Christmas From T1 Rex
item.description: Santa knows you’re eager to get a T1 line or Ethernet Connection this Christmas. He’s been busy upgrading his North Pole operations and is ready to fulfill your wishes from his high-tech workshop. Submit your telecommunications wish list to the elves today!
